text: Karsten Oelsch (born 13 April 1971) is a German gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Würzburg (district)
